Subject: wifi: nl80211: fix deadlock in nl80211_set_cqm_rssi (6.6.x)
To: stable@vger.kernel.org
Cc: "Léo Lam" <leo@leolam.fr>, "Philip Müller" <philm@manjaro.org>, "Johannes Berg" <johannes.berg@intel.com>
